headline.main: FIFA Chief 'Confident' of Video Officials at World Cup
headline.print_headline: FIFA Chief 'Confident' of Video Officials at World Cup

lead_paragraph: The U.S. Federal Reserve's long-stalled 'liftoff' of interest rates may finally get airborne this year as policymakers from Chair Janet Yellen on Friday to regional leaders across the United States signaled that the era of easy money is drawing to a close.
